+where X is the bus number and Y is the CS number
+
+SPI 0 pins (MOSI, MISO, SCK, CS): PC0, PC1, PC2, PC3
+SPI 1 pins (MOSI, MISO, SCK, CS): PA15, PA16, PA14, PA13
+
+Parameters:
+
+param_spidev_spi_bus (int)
